0.query: Q1: Find the ethnicity and hair color of ad with - name Dior - posting-date: 22 Oct 2014 - city Kansas City
0.sparql: PREFIX qpr: <http://istresearch.com/qpr> SELECT ?ad ?ethnicity ?hair_color WHERE { ?ad a qpr:Ad ; qpr:name 'Dior' ; qpr:posting_date '22 Oct 2014' ; qpr:city 'Kansas City' ; qpr:ethnicity ?ethnicity ; qpr:hair_color ?hair_color .}

1.query: What is the phone number of the escort with - name: Ella - eye color: green - hair color: brown - city: Portland
1.sparql: PREFIX qpr: <http://istresearch.com/qpr> SELECT ?ad ?phone WHERE { ?ad a qpr:Ad ; qpr:name 'Ella' ; qpr:eye_color 'green' ; qpr:city 'Portland' ; qpr:hair_color 'brown' ; qpr:phone ?phone .}

2.query: What is the city of escort with: - name: Brandy - phone: 386-334-6213
2.sparql: PREFIX qpr: <http://istresearch.com/qpr> SELECT ?ad ?city WHERE { ?ad a qpr:Ad ; qpr:name 'Brandy' ; qpr:phone '386-334-6213' ; qpr:city ?city .}
